media:group.media:title: Listen again to worship talks - Sunday, 7th April 2024 - Part 1
media:group.media:description:
Worship talks from Trinity United Reformed Church, High Wycombe What we spoke and prayed about 1 year ago 🗓️. How does it relate to now, is it still relevant?
Join us for worship every Sunday #AllAreWelcome
- Subscribe to receive notifications 🔔 when we post new talks. - Like our talks ❤️ or leave a comment on your favourite message. 🙏 - Share this video with friends and family to spread the light of God's word. 🔄
Where to find us: https://goo.gl/maps/2TCLpBvVymaCcJeM6?coh=178571&entry=tt Website: https://www.trinity-urc.org.uk Podcasts: https://anchor.fm/trinitycoresend-1year-ago Twitter: https://twitter.com/trinity_urc Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/trinity_urc/ YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@TrinityHighWycombe What's on: https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/o/trinity-and-cores-end-united-reformed-churches-32072022553 Mastodon: https://mastodon.social/@trinityhighwycombe Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/trinityhighwycombe.bsky.social
Listen again to key parts of our services from 1 year ago 🗓️ Let these ageless truths grip your heart now just as they did for us one year ago. Share this throwback sermon with someone who needs a renewed sense of purpose and calling. 🙌🏼 His plans made long ago, still light our way beyond today! ☀️ The biblical wisdom and guidance within this video remains powerfully relevant
